
                             UPGRADE

From 6.0.0 and 6.0.1 to 6.0.2
-----------------------------
Download the latest PHProjekt 6.0.2 releases from http://phprojekt.com and
untar them into your existing installation:

 $ tar xzvf phprojekt-6.0.2.tar.gz

Go to your old PHProjekt installation URL:

 http://example.com/phprojekt/htdocs/

You will be redirected to the setup routine. Use the setup routine
to update PHProjekt. The standard setup will automatically update
your installation.
